{"tid":272783,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲少女: 我要做個 Programmer!","createTime":"2017-06-06T05:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T13:21:25.000Z","uid":53406,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d682afb8e2f3c2fc06ea92106195a4352addecec","tid":272783,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=45673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2F%3Fp%3D45673&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9799e0bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=45673</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>上街自救<br />\n不想長期寄人籬下，Clara 當時得一條路，打工賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n「我有出去揾寫程式嘅工，但冇乜成功過， 始終你講嘢差，都係說服唔到人用你。」<br />\n<br />\n香港IT人收入算不錯，但僱主不會請一個中五𡃁妹仔。另外，Freelance 寫程式也不少，但接 Job所需要的口才、人脈和經驗，她當時全部欠奉。<br />\n<br />\nClara沒有放棄，甚至，她所使用的解決方法，竟然是亞氏保加症患者最恐懼的 &mdash; 社交。<br />\n<br />\n「有啲事情係練出來，自從出走以來，我一星期出去七晚，可能見朋友，可能去飲酒，去參加活動。其實會越來越純熟。」<br />\n<br />\n每逢周五傍晚，中環3號碼頭對出位置，都有個名為「Friday Beer Bay」的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">那裡九成是外國人</span>，多數是本地Tech Startup打工的技術人，聊的話題離不開Programming 或自己的Project。<br />\n<br />\n「喺度認識了一班programmer，遇到技術問題，我可以問佢地，佢地識嘅一定會教我。」<br />\n<br />\n偶然也有些<span style=\"color: red;\">外國來的高層</span>，他們日間出席會議、論壇，晚間到這裡邊吹海風邊飲啤酒，揾朋友吹水聊天，輕鬆一番。<br />\n<br />\n「其實也不一定要有什麼，識下朋友，大家傾吓人生，可能咁就過一晚。」<br />\n<br />\n日子有功，她跟陌生人社交，早已變得駕輕就熟。過去兩年，她接過不少本地Startup的技術外包，賺夠錢自己租房，不用再寄人籬下。<br />\n<br />\n後來，Clara更找到一分長工，還自己開發了一個社交媒體分析系統，算是她的第一個「Baby」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家要花4年讀cs, 學一堆數, algorithm, OS, 衝FYP等等<br />\nfresh grad時頭髮都甩唔少先有18K offer<br />\n一個17歲女識幾隻資訊科技洋腸就可以入Startup做<br />\n前途可能好過你地<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db35c7b160c37e3bad36af6580dfb08bf494bc83","tid":272783,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/claire-closeup-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fclaire-closeup-1.jpg&h=8fa911c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/claire-office-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fclaire-office-1.jpg&h=83d87db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/central-pier-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fcentral-pier-2.jpg&h=d0d9ade4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71c34695c08a4e832aa228d1dd4472188c4f24c5","tid":272783,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"磨牙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d626250063e6af0b6a928fff7785c13d3ff3ea0b","tid":272783,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0df04300cfd430e30de5efa0b442736b270e42","tid":272783,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"條女做女同事會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d170511224ee68d743e3ed3a1f080a2a84393243","tid":272783,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"平到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14feea91b9ded9de5a67621d7d3854a3f2ab227d","tid":272783,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dae1b48b9231b1fbbe5885dab13cd82606dc5c20","tid":272783,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"條女據聞有亞氏保加症<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>由於學校在調景嶺區，機緣巧合認識了孫柏文 &mdash; 當時的區議員助理。<br />\n<br />\n「之前就識佢。離家出走後冇晒錢，唔知點好，就去揾佢。」<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文是智庫獅子山學會的創辦人，同時是財演、馬主，身份多，人脈廣，別看他平日瘋癲，想不到觀察力頗強，他跟 Clara 談了幾句，就已看出了她可能是 Asperger（亞氏保加症），還直接問了她。<br />\n<br />\n「當時嚇了一跳，我的確係有啲。」<br />\n<br />\n孫柏文介紹Clara到智庫做暑期工，擴闊她的生活圈子。兩人年紀相差廿幾年，關係亦師亦友，對她影響頗大。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/claire01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fclaire01.jpg&h=8ea6d810&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fc55f73a3b0ce1d6d48b31b02971fc652f3cbca","tid":272783,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"條女而家係邊做?"},{"pid":"e1664a66272dd439264fd58e2ea800a5833b4bdc","tid":272783,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"樓上班友好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7360eaad13dd056551652cd9198957fc45c7e69","tid":272783,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"咁細個就想乞食？"},{"pid":"0bc0cb59fd765e9f4dcc48ec1da290977c3fd60b","tid":272783,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁細個就想乞食？</blockquote><br />\n你班毒撚就乞食<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=1139c508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n識programming既女仔好搶手<br />\n做到30歲話唔定已經嫁左比洋腸移民去外國做上等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b071c3c42b79597427bc04bc0d66336be39c290","tid":272783,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"有西何止係八達通<br />\n直頭可以當黑卡咁用"},{"pid":"4cb459ee3f9fde1bd5e353f9f9ef377d9b832813","tid":272783,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"女人+亞氏保加症+每晚會去飲酒/參加活動+資優生+寫programming+識好多外國人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfd60abed534d1cf6e4f431d498d006e2576918","tid":272783,"uid":79137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"亞視保家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6df2daa09efeb5a2663a5c552883b406e6361a","tid":272783,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"其他亞氏保加症既人係咪垃圾呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80af891816f9b20b05a8b85721cbe73810e04c07","tid":272783,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他亞氏保加症既人係咪垃圾呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認啦嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6888e202a21c74d4acc0694ad055100f6174d5f8","tid":272783,"uid":51411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"有亞氏保加症都敢咁積極社交<br />\n剩係呢樣都屌打其他u grad it人啦<br />\nD人成日怨人靠關係&gt;學歷 <br />\n事實係建立社交網絡同入u比 我覺得入u易好多"},{"pid":"231711c56fbc8ada175045b14db38a88a0893a5b","tid":272783,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有亞氏保加症都敢咁積極社交<br />\n剩係呢樣都屌打其他u grad it人啦<br />\nD人成日怨人靠關係&gt;學歷 <br />\n事實係建立社交網絡同入u比 我覺得入u易好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條女講乜你就信乜，真係亞氏保加症點可能晚晚出去social，好明顯同港女鍾意自稱抑鬱一樣想引人注意"},{"pid":"75e66acb9e7711cbaf2cbfe9592667b57604f81c","tid":272783,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"先唔講其他，著到咁搏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee91f329bd866456b335bd8fb7f54a598c28501","tid":272783,"uid":3643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:26:40.000Z","msg":"酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d8ce5affa5f8c59daa8fd21f64e9ae828867a4","tid":272783,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"咁撚肥都可以冇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8ae9107ffd2d403ed4a2d0c21d802333e0d02d","tid":272783,"uid":36651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"未入個post已經諗返起mingjai條片"},{"pid":"877278740b25019acb837e59fb2a10b4f31875af","tid":272783,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/claire-closeup-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fclaire-closeup-1.jpg&h=8fa911c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/claire-office-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fclaire-office-1.jpg&h=83d87db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/central-pier-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fcentral-pier-2.jpg&h=d0d9ade4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢部機上面啲code，styling好似麻麻喎"},{"pid":"baffc65d7d17c71591da1a6232e080716d50a268","tid":272783,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先唔講其他，著到咁搏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係點引人信"}]}